  ],
  "remarks": "Vyacheslav Petushenko is the Chairman of the Board of State Company “Avtodor”, which is the Russian state infrastructure and highway service company. “Avtodor” has signed an agreement to provide the right to free travel on toll roads for vehicles transporting aid to the zone of Russia’s illegal war of aggression against Ukraine. In addition, “Avtodor” is actively involved in reconstructing many roads in Ukrainian territories which have been occupied by Russia. President Putin has taken note of the work of “Avtodor” specialists, who are involved in the restoration of infrastructure in occupied areas. The aim of such actions is to integrate the occupied territories into Russia by building infrastructural objects. As the Chairman of the Board of State Company “Avtodor”, Vyacheslav Petushenko is implementing actions or policies which undermine the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
  "birth_info": [
